    <item>
      <title>希腊将取消部分零售客户银行费用，议会批准预算</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/greece-scrap-some-bank-fees-retail-customers-parliament-approves-budget-2024-12-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[希腊总理基里亚科斯·米佐塔基斯周日表示，作为帮助家庭应对生活成本危机的措施之一，希腊将取消部分零售交易的银行费用和收费。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/greece-scrap-some-bank-fees-retail-customers-parliament-approves-budget-2024-12-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 20:07:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据《华尔街日报》报道，总部位于波士顿的伯克希尔山银行和布鲁克林银行正在洽谈合并</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/boston-based-banks-berkshire-hills-brookline-talks-combine-wsj-reports-2024-12-14/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《华尔街日报》周六援引知情人士的话报道称，总部位于波士顿的地区性银行伯克希尔山银行和布鲁克林银行正在进行合并谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/boston-based-banks-berkshire-hills-brookline-talks-combine-wsj-reports-2024-12-14/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Dec 2024 16:50:32 GMT</pubDate>
